was spoiled.

297
00:16:40,346 --> 00:16:41,460
Are you kidding?

298
00:16:41,745 --> 00:16:43,312
The mother of my children

299
00:16:43,317 --> 00:16:45,310
with the reason for my children!

300
00:16:45,497 --> 00:16:47,780
This is gonna be the
greatest party ever!

301
00:16:48,267 --> 00:16:49,260
Oh, yeah!

302
00:16:49,517 --> 00:16:51,263
Duff beer is sponsoring the party,

303
00:16:51,437 --> 00:16:53,490
featuring new Duff Champagne

304
00:16:53,506 --> 00:16:55,190
the beer of champagnes!

305
00:16:55,565 --> 00:16:56,942
Oh, my God!

306
00:16:57,088 --> 00:16:59,963
It's like Christmas in December.
Let's celebrate now.

307
00:17:00,865 --> 00:17:02,811
Stop, Homer! Please!

308
00:17:03,798 --> 00:17:04,891
