316
00:17:24,487 --> 00:17:26,282
Thank God I figured it out

317
00:17:26,288 --> 00:17:28,292
before I did anything stupid.

318
00:17:30,488 --> 00:17:31,363
Oh, right.

319
00:17:36,698 --> 00:17:38,241
Oh, my God! I'm not dead!

320
00:17:40,986 --> 00:17:43,091
Homie, this is your party!

321
00:17:44,847 --> 00:17:46,092
This is great!

322
00:17:46,218 --> 00:17:48,311
I must be the first
gullible husband

323
00:17:48,398 --> 00:17:51,380
