of surprise party planning

324
00:17:51,578 --> 00:17:54,373
and think it was my wife
having an affair.

325
00:17:59,995 --> 00:18:03,541
Keep it up, people.
The night is young!

326
00:18:05,097 --> 00:18:06,623
